\fs32 \cf2 There\'92s a lot you can do with theme.json via the Site Editor, meaning you only need to edit it for more advanced settings. Or when you\'92re {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.advancedcustomfields.com/blog/wordpress-custom-theme-development/"}}{\fldrslt \cf8 building a theme from scratch}}, of course.\
